name: Welcome to Web3: Token 002
description:
Keep this glossary handy as you traverse the web3 world.

A few bonus terms and lessons: 
1. This NFT is considered a "large edition" because there are 1,000 minted. NFTs can come in any number editions, and typically the lower the edition, the more valuable it is in context of the broader artists work.

2. Take notice of gas fees (or transaction fees). When completing this transaction, be sure to read and understand the fees associated, which are only fractions of cents on Tezos (the blockchain associated to Hen) but can range up to $100 USD on Etherium-based marketplaces such as Opensea.

Welcome to Web3 is a project to help newcomers better understand and engage in Web3/NFTs/Crypto.
